name: IntentResolutionResult
desc: An object that matches a parameter of an intent, or information about why your service can’t determine a value for the parameter.

items.name: needsValue
items.desc: The service must have a value for this parameter, but the intent doesn’t include one.

items.name: notRequired
items.desc: The intent doesn’t include a value for this parameter, but the server can proceed without one.

items.name: unsupported
items.desc: The server doesn’t support this parameter.
